WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:09.600
Under Section 17A, if an employee or third party gives a bribe to obtain business, liability cascades upward.

00:10.000 --> 00:18.500
The organization and its directors are automatically liable unless they can prove they had 'Adequate Procedures' in place—

00:19.000 --> 00:21.000
specifically, the T.R.U.S.T. principles.